text: Elsie-Jane Blundell (née Wraighte; born August 1990) is a British Labour politician who has been Member of Parliament (MP) for Heywood and Middleton North since 2024. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1990 births Category:UK MPs 2024–present Category:Labour Party (UK) MPs Category:People from Cumbria
